MT_RET_REQUEST_REQUOTE: Requote in response to the request.
MT_RET_REQUEST_PRICES: Prices in response to the request.
MT_RET_REQUEST_PLACED: An order placed as a result of the request.
MT_RET_REQUEST_AT_DISABLED_CLIENT: Autotrading disabled on the client side.
MT_RET_REQUEST_FROZEN: Modification failed due to order or position being close to market.
MT_RET_REQUEST_LIMIT_ORDERS: Reached the limit on the number of orders.
MT_RET_REQUEST_INVALID_CLOSE_VOLUME: Volume to be closed exceeds the current volume of the position.
MT_RET_REQUEST_CLOSE_ORDER_EXIST: Order to close the position already exists.
MT_RET_REQUEST_LIMIT_POSITIONS: The number of open positions simultaneously present on an account can be limited by the settings of a group.
MT_RET_REQUEST_LONG_ONLY: The request is rejected, because the Only long positions are allowed rule is set for the symbol  (IMTConSymbol::TRADE_LONGONLY).
MT_RET_REQUEST_SHORT_ONLY: The request is rejected, because the Only short positions are allowed rule is set for the symbol (IMTConSymbol::TRADE_SHORTONLY).
MT_RET_REQUEST_CLOSE_ONLY: The request is rejected, because the Only position closing is allowed rule is set for the symbol (IMTConSymbol::TRADE_CLOSEONLY).
MT_RET_REQUEST_PROHIBITED_BY_FIFO: Position closure is not allowed by the FIFO rule.
